metadata.name: A Muse In Wonderland
metadata.description:
This work is a a 1/1 unique, and hand signed, edition. A scenic fusion of abstraction, figurative, and landscape. AI concepted, Collaged and digitally painted on tablet, in photoshop. It combines my traditional painting and digital abstracts as reference, and incorporating them with my ai figurative portraits, while fusing from inspiration, my own artistic stylization, with surrealism artist, Eileen Agar, pushing the boundaries and experimentation of my artistic style to date. 

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI Art show in history, featuring 100 artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
